{"tid":663142,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"樓上每逢禮拜日就裝修","createTime":"2018-05-13T04:58:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-13T09:54:03.000Z","uid":72718,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4f5eda4e2475f8384c33d8d0471d274aa73e38f0","tid":663142,"uid":72718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T04:58:39.000Z","msg":"已經連續3個禮拜都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n第1個禮拜係鑽加扑個地下<br />\n第2個禮拜係鑽<br />\n第3個禮拜姐係今日就dup野同批野<br />\n個個個禮拜都整3-4個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今日11點幾就俾佢嘈醒左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n平日佢就唔會整既<br />\n我估佢要返工返1-6<br />\n得禮拜日得閒先會整下<br />\n已經打過落管理處投訴<br />\n但管理處話要上黎聽下先知邊一戶<br />\n知道先至做到野<br />\n但樓上係整下停下<br />\n根本就搵唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實我都幾肯定係我樓上個單位<br />\n第1個禮拜係由廳整到入房<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實我唔介意佢晏就整<br />\n或者搵日一次過整哂佢唔好分幾個禮拜黎整<br />\n個個禮拜俾佢嘈醒真係CLS<br />\n我1個女仔又唔敢上去敲門同佢講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我可以點做"},{"pid":"a88b3bba58208e7e3602cc4a2dd2f71187fb8573","tid":663142,"uid":62367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T05:04:25.000Z","msg":"等佢再嘈就即刻打俾管理處叫佢地上黎聽<br />\n<br />\n係<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">即刻</span></span>，記住唔好拖"},{"pid":"300cf79fa157d5e88873d09d2f9c9e161852e53d","tid":663142,"uid":136494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-13T05:06:45.000Z","msg":"錄音 報警 星期日裝修好似係犯法的"},{"pid":"e444b9cf8cee68db1557a7c23b97799ae4754b98","tid":663